<bibRefCitation author="Carter, D. C. &amp; P. G. Dolan" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" pagination="1 - 136" refId="ref8084" refString="Carter, D. C., and P. G. Dolan. 1978. Catalog of type specimens of Neotropical bats in selected European museums. Special Publications, Museum Texas Tech University 15: 1 - 136." type="journal article" year="1978">Carter and Dolan, 1978</bibRefCitation>
